# Force GitHub Linguist to count only the Rust source tree.
# Anything that isn't src/ or top-level Rust manifests is build infrastructure,
# vendored test scaffolding, or documentation — none of it should skew the
# language stats.

# --- Test scaffolding ----------------------------------------------------
/test-servers/**           linguist-vendored
/data/**                   linguist-vendored

# --- Build / packaging ---------------------------------------------------
/Dockerfile                linguist-vendored
/pkg/**                    linguist-vendored
/HomebrewFormula/**        linguist-vendored
/scripts/**                linguist-vendored
/.github/**                linguist-vendored

# --- Documentation site --------------------------------------------------
/docs/**                   linguist-documentation
/overrides/**              linguist-vendored
/mkdocs.yml                linguist-vendored
/AGENTS.md                 linguist-documentation
/CLAUDE.md                 linguist-documentation
/CHANGELOG.md              linguist-documentation
/README.md                 linguist-documentation

# --- Catch-all by extension ----------------------------------------------
# Any HTML/CSS/JS/Python/Ruby/PHP/Shell/Dockerfile/YAML/JSON/Markdown anywhere
# in the tree is vendored test data, packaging, or docs — never Rust.
*.html                     linguist-vendored
*.htm                      linguist-vendored
*.css                      linguist-vendored
*.js                       linguist-vendored
*.py                       linguist-vendored
*.rb                       linguist-vendored
*.php                      linguist-vendored
*.sh                       linguist-vendored
*.dockerfile               linguist-vendored
Dockerfile*                linguist-vendored
*.conf                     linguist-vendored
*.yml                      linguist-vendored
*.yaml                     linguist-vendored
*.json                     linguist-vendored
*.toml                     linguist-vendored
*.md                       linguist-documentation
*.txt                      linguist-vendored
